==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|hei|lang=enm}}; probably a natural expression, as may be inferred from its presence with similar meaning in many unrelated languages: for example,Burmese {{term|ဟေး|lang=my|sc=Mymr|tr=hei}}, Finnish {{term|hei|lang=fi}}, Unami ''hè'', and Mandarin Chinese {{term|哎|lang=cmn|sc=Hani|tr=āi}}, and various sound-alikes as Roman [[eho]], Greek {{term|εἴα|tr=eia|lang=grc}}, Latin {{term|eia|lang=la}}, Dutch {{term|he|lang=nl}}, German {{term|hei|lang=de}}.

